title: Paulo Coelho, Part 2: Your Journey of Self-Discovery
description: Oprah’s conversation with best-selling author Paulo Coelho continues from his home in Switzerland. In Part 2, Paulo shares his unique spiritual journey and how he never lost faith in his personal dream.
author: podcasts@own.oprah.com (Oprah)
